<P>
   PARTYIDEAS _ A pretty table goes a long way in making your party
special. And it can be fun to design. ``I love to entertain. My
husband says I'm like a little girl planning a tea party,'' says
Jan Rudd of Beavercreek, who is known for her imaginative parties.
Her most recent dinner party transported guests to Provence.
``We've spent time in Provence and we love it,'' Rudd explains.
(Moss, Dayton Daily News). 7.
</P>
