   BASKETBALL/COLLEGES
</P>
<P>
   BKN-HAWKS-BLAZERS _ Advancing the Hawks at Portland, focusing on
former guard Steve Smith facing the Hawks for the first time since
his trade last summer. (Denberg, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
