<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-12 22:53 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8312 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r s BC-BBN-MODESTI-COLUMN-LA     11-12 0727
